metadata.name: IN YOUR EYES
metadata.description:
There is the blue skies in your eyes,  
This dreamy look is very nice,  
I see your inner light, it shines,  
Even better than the sunrise.   

Photo was taken by Masha Kozhdan. Minsk, May 2021.

Model: Liza Belaya (@_liza_belaya)
